subject: Happy New Year 2024..
body:
Happy New Year 2024..
Your payment falls into the category  of the first quarter of 2024
payment list. You are advised to inform us if you have received  above
$5MIllion into your bank account so that we can maintain your personal
account for the transfer but if you have not received such a huge
amount automatically, the bank will open an online bank account where
your funds can be wired into immediately.
Thanks.
Dominique Williams

subject: Re:   Happy New Year 2024..
body:
Happy New Year! Thank you for the information. Can you please provide more details about the payment list and how I can ensure that the transfer goes smoothly?

Best wishes,
Eldon

subject: Thanks for your urgent response to my email.
body:
Dear Eldon,

Thanks for your urgent response to my email, your email was among the fraud
victims selected to be paid in the first quarter of 2024.  All I need from
you is your full information in order to process your payment.

*Your full name, address, Telephone Number and Identification*, so that we
will do all the paperwork for the claim of the funds.

Thanks and get back to us with the requested information.

Dominique Williams.

subject: Re: Thanks for your urgent response to my email.
body:
Hello Dominique,
Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate the opportunity to claim the funds. Could you please provide more details about the process and how soon I can expect to receive the payment? Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Eldon
